Space... Space never changes...

Thousands of years have passed since humanity reached for the stars beyond and even after leaving planet Earth, mankind has far reigned kingdom to keep peace
in the final frontier. But now Sir Herrington, the King of Earth has passed and the young heir is not yet of age.
It is up to the Space Council of Space to choose a new ruler for the galaxies. As a dedicated member of the council you consider yourself fit
for the throne, but now it is up to you to claim enough trust from your associates to claim the throne.

Gain influence and fulfill their demands to gain their endorsement to become the new ruler of...
SUSIPALATSI
